{"id": 1679, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今，你觉得什么样的信息才算“有价值”？", "description": "在信息的汪洋里，你都是怎样浪里淘沙的", "record_count": 2636, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170510104104to9huF7JHNlSzQ4P.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-20T17:00:35Z", "options": [{"id": 205824, "content": "以 (让人能看到更多) 为目的的信息", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 944645}, {"id": 205825, "content": "期末的重点？不废话，就是干", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 785228}, {"id": 206081, "content": "具有前端意识的，开阔未来视野的东西。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037161}, {"id": 205826, "content": "和自身生活或工作息息相关的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1222204}, {"id": 206082, "content": "中立的，有系统分析，观点独特的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037165}, {"id": 205827, "content": "能够让我开拓眼界，或者思维的信息", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1266588}, {"id": 206339, "content": "跟生活息息相关、实用实在的，例如学业、职业、业余爱好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037468}, {"id": 207619, "content": "明确经过对方实践的\r\n包括引用内容", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040940}, {"id": 205828, "content": "有趣的，可以收获一定知识，技能，思维的提升，或者甚至仅情绪上感官上能够带来丰富和满足的", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1030994}, {"id": 205829, "content": "不是明天就过期的信息。而是能够作为严肃主题议论文的近期参考用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599658}, {"id": 206085, "content": "我需要的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1035537}, {"id": 205830, "content": "能提升个人认知的适应规律的知识", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036727}, {"id": 206086, "content": "不虚伪的，真实，讲明立场和来源的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 189259}, {"id": 206343, "content": "精练的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680656}, {"id": 207111, "content": "有趣的，比如很多新闻都喜欢分类。但是我特别讨厌明星的八卦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039593}, {"id": 205832, "content": "不鸡汤，不八卦，不妄语", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955981}, {"id": 206344, "content": "跟生活息息相关、实用实在的，例如学业、职业、业余爱好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037468}, {"id": 206089, "content": "真实有效的金融类实时信息", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 533987}, {"id": 228361, "content": "适合自己的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589122}, {"id": 205834, "content": "有变现的价值", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852060}, {"id": 205835, "content": "真实，有用，出于善意的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522241}, {"id": 205836, "content": "不扯", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 104159}, {"id": 206604, "content": "我关注的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038139}, {"id": 206093, "content": "高考答案", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022726}, {"id": 205838, "content": "哪怕是编造、猜测的，只要能让我信服五秒以上，都是有价值、没白花时间看的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 381503}, {"id": 205839, "content": "我不知道的知识", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 523065}, {"id": 206095, "content": "每个人都有自己的价格定义，对自己有用的便是有价值的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1035729}, {"id": 206607, "content": "与利益无关，纯属来表达个人观点，并且对社会有积极影响作用的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038195}, {"id": 205840, "content": "内部消息", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955981}, {"id": 207120, "content": "简短精湛的分析", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039612}, {"id": 206097, "content": "对自己有帮助和有思想的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1002018}, {"id": 205842, "content": "新颖一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697574}, {"id": 206099, "content": "不标题党", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 936251}, {"id": 206868, "content": "真实、结合实际、反应事实的信息才有价值", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039160}, {"id": 206101, "content": "能让你活得更好的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037206}, {"id": 205846, "content": "能提高月考成绩的方法", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 983300}, {"id": 206102, "content": "哪儿好吃?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037207}, {"id": 206103, "content": "我不知道的，并且跟我相关对我有用的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037209}, {"id": 205848, "content": "对我有用", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 872416}, {"id": 206104, "content": "知识点！各种科技原理！知识改变命运！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1030898}, {"id": 206105, "content": "明白讲述的事实或者亲身经历", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1031053}, {"id": 206106, "content": "对我有用的，不管是现在有用，还是未来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037218}, {"id": 206362, "content": "生活中思考过但没深究的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197691}, {"id": 206618, "content": "我敢兴趣的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038236}, {"id": 207642, "content": "和我有关的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918125}, {"id": 207898, "content": "能变现的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1006402}, {"id": 206107, "content": "干货", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034240}, {"id": 206108, "content": "整合的逻辑的，有前因后果追根溯源的史观贯穿的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 206621, "content": "衡量信息是否有价值显然取决于每个人的价值观啊～对我来说，能让我哭让我笑让我的大脑运转起来进行思考，在接收碎片化信息同时潜移默化地改变我的思维及生活方式的信息，才算“有价值”。“价值”的体现也不一定都是正向的。谁能说导致我犯错的信息就没有价值呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038253}, {"id": 206110, "content": "考试考的到", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 974719}]}